<L>__{int day: flamingo hotel suite (1955)}
<A>__{a whole entourage precedes fredo and his v.i.p. party of michael, hagen and neri. great fuss is made. they are being shown into the hotel's 'special' suite.}
<C>__{fredo}
<D>__{you look wonderful, kid; really wonderful. that doctor did some job on your face.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{you look good, too.}
<A>__{they enter the suite.}
<C>__{fredo}
<D>__{nice, eh?}
<A>__{fredo is as excited as a kid, snapping orders at the bellboys, waiters and maids.}
<C>__{fredo}
<P>__{(hurrying into the bedroom)}
<D>__{kid, take a look see.}
<A>__{michael gives a look to hagen, and continues into the bedroom. there is an enormous circular bed on a huge platform, mirrors to each side. fredo points upward. a view into a large ceiling mirror.}
